Pre-Game Insights: Collin Benjamin emphasized the importance of working on coming out from the back tactically and noted it was a learning curve for the players.
Post-Match Reflections: Erastus Kalula expressed excitement about his national team debut and scoring, and acknowledged the need for team improvement.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Namibia will host Liberia on 5 June at the Orlando Stadium followed by their second encounter against Tunisia on 9 June 2024.
